###################
#  README corpus  #
###################

### OVERVIEW ###
* This folder contains the actual corpus.
* There are ten folders, one for every scenario. every folder contains one file per story for the scenario.

### DATA FORMAT ###
* All texts are tokenized and split into sentences. 
* All verbs are pos tagged and lemmatized automatically (Stanford Parser v3.5.0, http://nlp.stanford.edu/software/lex-parser.shtml).
* All tokens that are goverend by a verb are also lemmatized and pos tagged.
* We also give the dependency label for nouns that directly depend on a verb, as found by Stanford parser.
* Each of the stories has been annotated and converted to XML format.
* For more information about the xml format, please refer to InScript.dtd.